### 健康检查
GET http://localhost:8080/api/health

### 登录
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 城市列表
GET http://localhost:8080/api/cities

### 成都景点
GET http://localhost:8080/api/cities/1/spots

### 成都美食
GET http://localhost:8080/api/cities/1/foods

### 规则版生成行程
POST http://localhost:8080/api/trip-plans/generate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "departureCity": "南京",
  "cityId": 1,
  "days": 3,
  "peopleCount": 2,
  "budgetLevel": "MEDIUM",
  "pace": "RELAXED",
  "interests": ["美食", "轻松"]
}

### AI 助手占位
POST http://localhost:8080/api/ai/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "我想从南京去成都玩 3 天"
}

